    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>我们请求你给予我们你的一部分。你身份的一部分。</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/bc942ac63023ea86dea177d585393418.poster.avif?t=1764073752\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/bc942ac63023ea86dea177d585393418.webm?t=1764073752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/bc942ac63023ea86dea177d585393418.mp4?t=1764073752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Mirror Layers 是一款第一人称社交恐怖游戏。</strong><br><br><br><br><strong>探索神秘的12号公寓，与其他玩家合作解决具有挑战性的谜题，并在“镜子”中求生——那是一个被悲剧污染、扭曲的现实。</strong></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>剧情</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/b23a60a14c9b168ad05ae6b89dea60ce.poster.avif?t=1764073752\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/b23a60a14c9b168ad05ae6b89dea60ce.webm?t=1764073752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/b23a60a14c9b168ad05ae6b89dea60ce.mp4?t=1764073752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在 Mirror Layers 中，玩家扮演的正是自己。<br>你收到了一份匿名邀请，要求你前往 Chandran 公寓——一座奇异的16层建筑，最近正在举办一些怪异的“密室逃脱”游戏。<br>你会加入这场游戏吗？</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>社交恐怖体验</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/e52fcecd9d82376ad2fe4c98c0623870.poster.avif?t=1764073752\" width=622 height=350 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/e52fcecd9d82376ad2fe4c98c0623870.webm?t=1764073752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/e52fcecd9d82376ad2fe4c98c0623870.mp4?t=1764073752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >要在 Mirror Layers 中推进游戏，你必须通过一个名为 Propaganda 的社交网络与其他玩家互动。在那里，你可以分享建议、观点，尤其是物品。<br>游戏还提供记笔记与拍照的工具；记住，共享即生存！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>谜题</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/dfeba66b234eab4a1ca62e77f86df5ec.poster.avif?t=1764073752\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/dfeba66b234eab4a1ca62e77f86df5ec.webm?t=1764073752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/dfeba66b234eab4a1ca62e77f86df5ec.mp4?t=1764073752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏的核心是不断升级的复杂谜题：在探索公寓的过程中，你可以收集并检查关键物品，以便与其及其环境进行互动。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong><i>试玩版</i></strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/4f93ae0754b5b9eea386246f27c538e8.poster.avif?t=1764073752\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/4f93ae0754b5b9eea386246f27c538e8.webm?t=1764073752\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1746440/extras/4f93ae0754b5b9eea386246f27c538e8.mp4?t=1764073752\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款试玩版只能让你一窥 Mirror Layers 的全貌。你知道吗？在 Chandran 公寓里，有一面非常奇特的镜子……<br>想了解更多，请访问 Mirror Layers 的 Steam 页面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>我已经接触到了。你呢？你在等什么？</i></strong></p>",
